snippet.title: Chrono Ghost  - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Chrono Ghost Site: http://www.nitetimestudios.com/chronoghost/
Press: http://nitetimestudios.com/press/

On January 4th 2019, you will have the chance to t traverse through unique natural environments full of obstacles and challenges.

Chrono Ghost for PC, Mac, and Linux!

Music in the trailer has been copyrighted and was created by PeriBang Records
PeriBang Records: https://www.peribangrecords.com/ 

Get the Soundtrack at:
https://www.amazon.com/Chrono-Ghost-Original-Game-Soundtrack/dp/B07JXYJHZP/

Follow NITETIME Studios: 
Twitter:  @NITETIMEStudios
Instagram: @NITETIMEStudios
Website: http://www.nitetimestudios.com
